{"tid":1438424,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"拉撚曬你班暴徒！","createTime":"2019-08-09T18:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T18:20:41.000Z","uid":182596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6d3648104d862c0f050f0ab0d93eb180c04a0709","tid":1438424,"uid":182596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:19:47.000Z","msg":"說好的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一次比一次難拉</span>人</span><br />\n大佬啊 人地依家鳩拉人 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">理撚得你街坊定義士 </span><br />\n係唔係都拉左先 告唔入最多咪遲啲靜靜雞放左你<br />\n用<span style=\"color: red;\">被捕人仕嘅數字</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">反對通知書</span>兇班和理非 (被捕不等於告得入)<br />\n等勇武無support 再慢慢拉啲拉啲<br />\n拉夠1000個已經贏成條街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">be water</span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好戀戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">跑得慢嘅企後少少/早啲跑<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">驚青嘅企埋一邊唔好變左人肉roadblock </span><br />\n<br />\nSorry未開過post 1999但每次見到有人比狗擒左都好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c8693c4fff4349ba51f769643f89ea6156ea52","tid":1438424,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:20:40.000Z","msg":"屌你老味 而家燒吓衣都分分鐘俾人告縱火<br />\n講經咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf44745576e2921680836fc4bdf2a70f65b0e688","tid":1438424,"uid":182596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:20:41.000Z","msg":"講到1999希望大家明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}